Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.18,0:22:54.81,ED2-CN W,,0,0,0,,一如既往
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.81,0:22:56.60,ED2-CN W,,0,0,0,,总是偷着掖着
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.60,0:22:58.31,ED2-CN W,,0,0,0,,那无需质疑的神情
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.31,0:22:59.69,ED2-CN W,,0,0,0,,真的太直接了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.69,0:23:00.98,ED2-CN W,,0,0,0,,你的表情
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.98,0:23:02.65,ED2-CN W,,0,0,0,,阿谀奉承
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.65,0:23:04.36,ED2-CN W,,0,0,0,,到底重复了多少次
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.36,0:23:08.70,ED2-CN W,,0,0,0,,难道你会不知道无礼的言语吗？
Comment: 0,0:23:08.70,0:23:08.70,ED-CN-2 W,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.70,0:23:11.03,ED-CN-2 W,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}将心灵汲取修缮
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.03,0:23:11.99,ED-CN-2 W,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}是非常重要的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.99,0:23:13.12,ED2-CN W,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,100)\bord2.44\blur4\c&HFFFFFF&\1a&H00&\fs108\3c&HAC9379&\4c&HBD6BFA&\4a&HFF&\frz5.89\pos(1018,908)\fsp24}无论是谁
