Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.83,0:23:15.96,ED-CN-2 W,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}不会向任何人透露
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.00,0:23:16.46,ED2-CN W,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,100)\bord2.44\blur4\c&HFFFFFF&\1a&H00&\fs108\3c&HAC9379&\4c&HBD6BFA&\4a&HFF&\frz4.69\fsp24\pos(960,850)}是这样吧？
